        "\n",
        "## La Sinfon√≠a El√©ctrica del Cuerpo\n",
        "\n",
        ":::: {.columns}\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.column width=\"45%\"}\n",
        "El **Electrocardiograma (ECG)** es el ritmo del coraz√≥n, nuestro tambor principal."
      ],
